<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

       
        <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                background-color: #f8f9fa;
                color: #333;
                overflow-x: hidden;
            }
            .container {
                width: 80%;
                margin: 0 auto;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 50px 0;
            }
            .container h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                animation: flyIn 1s ease-out;
            }
            .container p {
                font-size: 18px;
                color: #666;
                margin-bottom: 50px;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                animation: flyIn 1.5s ease-out;
            }
            .row {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            .column {
                width: 45%;
                text-align: left;
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                animation: flyIn 2s ease-out;
            }
            .column img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            }
            .column h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                animation: flyIn 2.5s ease-out;
            }
            .column p {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #666;
                line-height: 1.6;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                animation: flyIn 3s ease-out;
            }
            .contact {
                margin-top: 50px;
                text-align: left;
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                animation: flyIn 3.5s ease-out;
            }
            .contact h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                animation: flyIn 4s ease-out;
            }
            .contact p {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #666;
                line-height: 1.6;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
                position: relative;
                animation: flyIn 4.5s ease-out;
            }

            @keyframes flyIn {
                0% {
                    opacity: 0;
                    transform: translateX(-100%);
                }
                100% {
                    opacity: 1;
                    transform: translateX(0);
                }
            }
        </style>

    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Welcome to Wanderlust, your ultimate travel companion. We are passionate about exploring the world and helping you create unforgettable travel experiences.</p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="column">
                    <img alt="Skyscrapers with a cloudy sky background" src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.TYPryvWreYLzXYbqgXzYDwHaFH?w=290&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" />
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>At Wanderlust, our mission is to inspire and empower travelers to explore the world with confidence. We provide comprehensive travel guides, tips, and resources to help you plan your perfect trip. Whether you're seeking adventure, relaxation, or cultural immersion, we are here to make your travel dreams a reality.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="column">
                    <img alt="Team of people working together in an office" src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.e2cRim0Wi3I2U2WEpt6kUAHaFF?w=352&h=197&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" />
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded by a group of avid travelers, Wanderlust was born out of a shared love for discovering new places and cultures. Our team has traveled to over 50 countries, and we bring our firsthand experiences and insights to you. We believe that travel has the power to transform lives, and we are dedicated to making travel accessible and enjoyable for everyone.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="contact">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions, feedback, or need assistance with your travel plans, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. You can contact us via email at support@wanderlust.com or call us at (123) 456-7890. We look forward to hearing from you and helping you embark on your next adventure!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
 